::Ramulus/DeathScythe::

Ramulus frowns. Where would he get a portable replicator in this heap? He 
sighs.

"It'll have to wait then," he says to Iris, "We have no replicators here."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DeathScythe growls at Zyber, the idea that she now thought that two Maximals 
had taken him down getting him slightly mad. It didn't matter, though, she'd 
be dead soon enough...

"I was flying," he said, "They took me by surprize. By the time I could 
react, my thrusters were out."

He nods at her second question. "Yes. I'll have some more."
